```1549525414 WARN Configurator.c:111 Got error [Failed to configure tunnel [WinFail.c:3059 DeleteUnicastIpAddressEntry(&table->Table[i]) [ERROR_ACCESS_DENIED]]] calling [Core_initTunnel], ignoring.```

If you see this, you need to run it from a command prompt in administrative mode.

When a node in your config is up, it will connect and just report an `Ok.` message.
The more OKs the more nodes you connected to.
